{"tid":344230,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普：劍指英超冠軍","createTime":"2017-08-02T06:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-02T08:53:28.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2aafd0414ca4002454fecc14a4d49d7bcf27a74","tid":344230,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:40:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/0/050/18683437050/18657807087_600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F0%2F050%2F18683437050%2F18657807087_600x399.jpg&h=0892f7b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=9V8l8fa56wF2ewEMC3kAMtU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=045f70ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】正在德國備戰的利物浦，即將出戰奧迪盃，與拜仁慕尼黑交手，翌日再鬥馬德里體育會或拿玻里，大戰之前，利物浦領隊高普談到球隊新球季的目標，就是英超冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n「對，我們是為了冠軍而戰。我們不會在沒有野心下開始新一季。我們必須有目標。」利物浦領隊高普（Jurgen Klopp）說，「這就是我們上季所做的。我們瞄準了冠軍，結果以第4名完成，但我認為我們現在有一個非常好的團隊。我們上季確實有一點不好運，我認為球隊可以踢得更好。希望一切都會順利，我們必須非常努力做好這件事。」<br />\n<br />\n球隊即將出戰拜仁慕尼黑，高普說，「我們正在努力備戰，所以對拜仁能達到甚麼是很重要的。拜仁絕對是一支頂級球隊，無論陣容怎樣也很強勁。從我的經驗來看，他們總是難踢的球隊，所以能見識他們的團隊我將會很高興。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"08068962a206fd4ba82a0061e6ba96208fc6f8d9","tid":344230,"uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:40:12.000Z","msg":"利物浦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"023921c7107ea7ebc8b1a7e96f6c5902fd20a677","tid":344230,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:40:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成地精"},{"pid":"fe65ac2a0265967eddbbab6d8cd59bc9013ddb88","tid":344230,"uid":91875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-02T06:41:40.000Z","msg":"癲左"},{"pid":"4111dda36b49d3fc4cc54e92de203ab2e4f328f4","tid":344230,"uid":36702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"rep